---
// Music Section - Full width layout
---

<div id="music" class="music-section">
  <!-- Text Block - Top center, full width -->
  <div class="music-text-banner">
    <p>I like all kinds of music. Although I don't have much musical talent, I've tried different things in music. I pursue the poetry and uncertainty in music.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Three images below - evenly spaced -->
  <div class="music-images-row">
    <!-- Piano -->
    <article class="music-image-card">
      <div class="card-inner">
        <img src="/photos/piano.png" alt="Piano" />
        <div class="image-overlay">
          <span>Obsessed with piano after watching The Legend of 1900 as a teen. Still chasing the skill to play it smoothly.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- Guzheng -->
    <article class="music-image-card">
      <div class="card-inner">
        <img src="/photos/guzheng.png" alt="Guzheng" />
        <div class="image-overlay">
          <span>Warm oriental guqin still life. Adds tranquil artistic texture to my personal site's bright dark UI.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- Gramophone -->
    <article class="music-image-card">
      <div class="card-inner">
        <img src="/photos/gramophone.png" alt="Gramophone" />
        <div class="image-overlay">
          <span>A warm-toned vinyl record player. Conveying my love for the timeless analog sound.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .music-section {
    width: 100%;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  /* Text Banner - Top center, full width */
  .music-text-banner {
    background: var(--color-bg, #ffffff);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border, rgba(229, 231, 235, 0.8));
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg, 16px);
    padding: var(--space-8) var(--space-12);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    box-shadow: inset 1px 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  }

  .music-text-banner p {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #4b5563;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* Three images row - evenly distributed */
  .music-images-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .music-image-card {
    border-radius: var(--radius-md, 12px);
    overflow: hidden;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08), rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.05));
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform 220ms ease, box-shadow 220ms ease;
    box-shadow: inset 1px 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  }

  .card-inner {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .card-inner img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: filter 0.25s ease, transform 0.25s ease;
    display: block;
  }

  .image-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: all 0.25s ease;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .image-overlay span {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    transform: translateY(6px);
    transition: transform 0.25s ease;
  }

  /* Hover Effect */
  .music-image-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: 0 25px 80px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.12), inset 1px 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  }

  .music-image-card:hover .card-inner img {
    filter: blur(2px) brightness(0.45);
    transform: scale(1.04);
  }

  .music-image-card:hover .image-overlay {
    opacity: 1;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55);
  }

  .music-image-card:hover .image-overlay span {
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .music-images-row {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .music-text-banner {
      padding: var(--space-6) var(--space-8);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .music-images-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .music-text-banner {
      padding: var(--space-6) var(--space-6);
    }

    .music-text-banner p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
